9
00:01:49,317 --> 00:01:49,567

10
00:01:54,072 --> 00:01:55,115
Inokuma...

11
00:01:55,115 --> 00:01:57,158
¡Inokuma no se levanta!

12
00:01:57,158 --> 00:01:58,576
